{"lastModified":1775211847986,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nA majestic 67 ft. custom catamaran featuring 5 VIP cabins, able to accommodate up to 10 people. WHITE CAPS combines luxury, comfort and style. The amount of volume that WHITE CAPS offers for socializing and relaxing will immediately impress you. She is a beauty that is sure to turn heads wherever she goes!","blueprint":{"name":"WHITE CAPS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc96a920-1aaa-11f0-b28e-516d6807fdee/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc968210-1aaa-11f0-b28e-516d6807fdee/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc9374d0-1aaa-11f0-b28e-516d6807fdee/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc96d030-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc960ce0-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc954990-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc971e50-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc95bec0-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc94d460-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc945f30-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3a0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fc97ba90-1aaa-11f0-b908-1534fe39c708/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image: